transcripts: [Music Playing] Early morning... we're already here at the gym. About to do some agility today. We're going to the batting cage , we gotta hit, if we hit we eat. If we don't hit, it's a struggle in there. I'm done with my day, I'm gonna go eat with my girlfriend, a couple of friends, follow me. I'm officially done well you guys take care and be safe, UA.
